title: RHOC That's Showbiz! + Summer House/VPR
itunes:title: RHOC That's Showbiz! + Summer House/VPR
description:
Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of Orange County, which concluded with a midseason trailler! The women also arrive in Cabo for their cast trip, where Emily snaps, Shannon shouts, Heather architects (?), and Noella arrives late to stir up trouble. Jen is also there. After RHOC, Danny touches on the VPR finale and the Summer House premiere-- Kyle and Amanda...whew!


SUMMER HOUSE: 44:02ish
